<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-line-height-alt:.75pt"><span style=3D"f=
ont-size:1.0pt;color:white">Good afternoon Lance, I=E2=80=99ve just tried t=
o call =E2=80=93 could you please call when convenient tomorrow. Unfortunat=
ely, your letter doesn=E2=80=99t address the specific concerns
 that Prendos has raised, or provide any consideration of the specific prov=
isions<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
