<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">All tenders are com=
plete and have accounted for all items detailed on the uncosted scope of wo=
rks provided by ASURNZ.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">In the comparative =
summary you will see that I have presented some line items in blue. This is=
 to indicate where the tenderer has provided a PC sum for this item.<o:p></=
o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Any questions which=
 you may have in relation to any of the specific items in the tender compar=
ison, please do not hesitate to ask.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Our recommendation =
is to settle the structural claim based on the most competitive tender resp=
onse provided by JLG. $419,434.08 Incl GST.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I look forward to f=
