<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good afternoon Raff=
aella &amp; All,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have just spoken =
with Abigail Collin re the forthcoming test results.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We expect the test =
results to be available to share with all parties by the end of next week. =
I have chased the provider to expedite this.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The preliminary rep=
ort from the Forensic Testing will contain the =E2=80=98raw data=E2=80=99 f=
rom the laboratory results, and the locations of the sample sites from wher=
e the tests were conducted.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As promised this pr=
eliminary report will be shared with all as soon as it is received and it w=
ill be followed by a fuller report which will provide Towers position on th=
e findings of the report.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you for your =
continued patience.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regards,<o:p></o:p>=
</span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant. <o:p></o:p><=
