<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-=
family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<div style=3D"border:none;border-top:solid windowtext 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0=
in 0in 0in">
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot=
;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">From:</span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-s=
pace"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-=
serif">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quo=
t;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">Grant
 Metson &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz">Grant.Metson@tower.=
co.nz</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Sent:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Tuesday, 14 =
October 2025 4:51 PM<br>
<b>To:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Raffaella del =
Prete &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:raffaellanz@icloud.com">raffaellanz@icloud.com<=
/a>&gt;<br>
<b>Cc:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Abigail Collin=
 &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Abigail.Collin@wynnwilliams.co.nz">Abigail.Collin@wy=
nnwilliams.co.nz</a>&gt;; Richard Hargreaves &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Richard.=
Hargreaves@wynnwilliams.co.nz">Richard.Hargreaves@wynnwilliams.co.nz</a>&gt=
;;
 Bryan Strong &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Bryan.Strong@tower.co.nz">Bryan.Strong@=
tower.co.nz</a>&gt;; Kelly Mason &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Kelly.Mason@tower.co=
.nz">Kelly.Mason@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;; Arna Neems &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Arna=
.Neems@tower.co.nz">Arna.Neems@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;; Lance
 O'Riley &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Lance.ORiley@tower.co.nz">Lance.ORiley@tower=
.co.nz</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Subject:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>RE: C9030=
6048 - Fire at 23 Mays Street, Devonport [WW-ACTIVE.FID3167762]</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello Raffaella,</s=
pan><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you for the e=
mail below.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We can confirm that=
 testing can commence at 2pm on Friday October 17.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We will test from s=
ample sites as required to complete a full and thorough determination of an=
y potential contamination, inclusive of all the areas which you have referr=
ed to below.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You may undertake y=
our own independent testing at any stage; however, Tower would only conside=
r reimbursement for testing which is - a) claim related &amp; b) testing wh=
ich is outside of that which Tower will
 complete.<span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am confident that=
 the Tower Insurance testing will be transparent, quantified by lab results=
, and adequate to provide comfort for all parties.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clarified scope =
of testing as follows:</span></u><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0in" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;ms=
o-list:l14 level1 lfo11">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">150mm diameter inspection portals cut in w=
all cavities of every room on the first floor at a height of 300 mm of floo=
r level and directly underneath the top plate.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li cl=
ass=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list=
:l14 level1 lfo11">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Testing of the roof cavity at the soffit j=
unction where potential contaminants may have risen through the wall cavity=
. Testing of the roof cavity at the apex where smoke may have accumulated.<=
/span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0i=
n;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l14 level1 lfo11">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Testing of the underside of the rear large=
 upper deck.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"=
margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l14 level1 lfo11">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Testing of the basement utilizing all expo=
sed framing cavities and 150mm testing portals cut into any remining ceilin=
g linings in the basemen area.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListPa=
ragraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l14 level1 lfo1=
1">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Any additional sample sites that we feel a=
re required during testing. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></li></ol>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">To ensure effect=
ual testing it would be beneficial if you could confirm the following:</spa=
n></u><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0in" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;ms=
o-list:l6 level1 lfo12">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">That the chlorine was located in the laund=
ry room downstairs at the time of the fire.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=
=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l6=
 level1 lfo12">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The quantity of the chlorine that was in t=
hat room at the time of the fire.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoLis=
tParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l6 level1 lf=
o12">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Where there any<span class=3D"apple-conver=
ted-space">&nbsp;</span><u>other chemicals</u><span class=3D"apple-converte=
d-space">&nbsp;</span>that were located in that same room, or anywhere else=
 downstairs. &nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></li></ol>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Beyond completing t=
esting and providing laboratory results as described above, I am certain th=
e most productive action we can make towards progressing the claim is to ha=
ve a meeting where we can discuss the
 overall claim response process, providing a forum for you to table any que=
stions, or concerns that you may hold. Those concerns can be responded to, =
and the responses can be documented via minutes with actions and agreements=
 detailed in the minutes providing
 a framework for moving forward with a pre-agreed and productive pathway. I=
 believe this would be very worthwhile and will provide us all with detail,=
 clarity, and documentation that we can all use to our benefit.</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Your lawyers and ad=
visors would of course be welcome to attend this meeting.</span><o:p></o:p>=
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I look forward to s=
eeing you again on Friday.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Kind Regards,</span=
><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant. &nbsp;&nbsp;=
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
